      <title>French Fintech Qonto寻求银行许可证，因为它针对2030年的200万客户</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-fintech-qonto-seeks-banking-license-it-targets-2-million-clients-by-2030-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[它周四表示，法国金融科技Qonto已在法国的银行监管机构申请了银行许可证，因为它试图扩大付款服务以提供贷款，储蓄和投资产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-fintech-qonto-seeks-banking-license-it-targets-2-million-clients-by-2030-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 12:55:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
